data.description: Fantastic investment opportunity in a prime location! This side-by-side duplex features a comfortable layout of 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and stack washer/dryer hookups in each apartment. The single-level design offers ease of movement. Convenience is the key with this property, as it offers easy access to BSU, making it perfect for students and faculty alike. The duplex offers carports, providing covered parking for your vehicles and protecting them from the elements. Storage closets are also available, allowing you to keep your belongings organized and easily accessible.  Fenced backyards and decks offer a space to relax while alley access provides additional convenience when it comes to parking.  Take advantage of this chance to add this duplex in a sought-after location to your investment portfolio or owner occupy and have second apartment help with mortgage payment.
